body_html: I'm seeing this too. Still seems worth fixing, doesn't it? Errors can be pretty discouraging even if (apparently) this one is harmless. I followed the commands in https://hub.docker.com/r/tensorflow/tensorflow/ in CPU mode btw, "docker run -it -p 8888:8888 tensorflow/tensorflow".
